@page
@model Friday_Film_Club.Pages.PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="privacy-container">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to Friday Film Club. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information in accordance with GDPR, accessibility for disabilities, and human rights.</p>

    <h2>GDPR Compliance</h2>
    <p>We are committed to complying with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). This means that we will:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Collect and process your personal data lawfully, fairly, and transparently.</li>
        <li>Only collect personal data that is necessary for the purposes for which it is being processed.</li>
        <li>Ensure that your personal data is accurate and kept up to date.</li>
        <li>Keep your personal data for no longer than is necessary for the purposes for which it is being processed.</li>
        <li>Protect your personal data against unauthorized or unlawful processing, accidental loss, destruction, or damage.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Accessibility for Disabilities</h2>
    <p>We are committed to ensuring that our website is accessible to everyone, including individuals with disabilities. We strive to adhere to the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1, which provide recommendations for making web content more accessible. Our efforts include:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Providing text alternatives for non-text content.</li>
        <li>Ensuring that our website is navigable and usable with a keyboard.</li>
        <li>Making our website content readable and understandable.</li>
        <li>Ensuring that our website is compatible with assistive technologies.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Human Rights</h2>
    <p>We are committed to respecting and promoting human rights in all aspects of our operations. This includes:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Respecting the privacy and dignity of all individuals.</li>
        <li>Ensuring that our practices do not discriminate against any individual or group.</li>
        <li>Promoting a safe and inclusive environment for all users of our website.</li>
        <li>Addressing any concerns or complaints related to human rights in a timely and effective manner.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy or how we handle your personal data, please contact us at:</p>
    <p>Email: support@fridayfilmclub.com</p>
    <p>Address: 123 Film Street, Movie City, Filmland</p>

    <p>Thank you for trusting Friday Film Club with your personal information. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that our website is accessible and inclusive for all users.</p>
</div>